	<title>Gadget development</title>
  <highlights>
    <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
            <para><emphasis role="bold"><link linkend="sect-Reference_Guide-Gadgets">Gadgets</link></emphasis></para>
          <para>Knowledge of default gadgets on the system or remote ones and how to create new ones, edit/delete/import them or view them on the dashboard, and more.</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para><emphasis role="bold"><link linkend="sect-Reference-Guide_Gadgets_Standard-WebApp">Standard WebApp for Gadget importer</link></emphasis></para>
          <para>Instruction on how to create a WebApp which has a standard structure processed by the Gadget importer.</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para><emphasis role="bold"><link linkend="sect-Reference_Guide-Setup_a_Gadget_Server">Set up a Gadget Server</link></emphasis></para>
           <para>Instructions on how to configure the gadget host and knowledge about security key for gadget container, gadget proxy and concat configuration.</para>
        </listitem>
